Class SharedLoginPage

  • java.lang.Object
    • SharedLoginPage
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    MeetingLoginPage, WebinarLoginPage

    public class SharedLoginPage
extends java.lang.Object
    The Class SharedLoginPage, which defines the objects found on the Login page for GoToMeeting and for GoToWebinar. Additionally, it may include helper methods.
